snippet.title: MOTOGP™24 Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Mark your calendar for May 2, 2024 – it's a date you won't miss! 
The adrenaline rush of #MotoGP24 is coming featuring the most authentic #MotoGP universe, including the Riders Market, MotoGP™ Stewards, the new LiveGP Championship and much more. 
It only happens in #MotoGP24! #MotoGPvideogame #MotoGP
